Brittany Ashton Holmes https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brittany_Ashton_Holmes 0 Brittany Ashton Holmes (born February 27, 1989 in California) is an American former child actress best known for playing Darla in the 1994 feature-film adaptation of The Little Rascals. She also appeared as Amy Carter in the 1996 film Inhumanoid and retired from acting later that year. Holmes currently resides in Los Angeles and is working on getting a degree in political science.
